1. Installation		2. Configuration		3. Credits
-------------------------------------------------------------------
Installing Excursion is easier than ever! By following these few 
steps; your Excursion website will be up and running in no time.

	1.	Upload the package to your web server
	
	2.	Create a MySQL database (or use a currently existing 
		database), and run install.sql
		
	3.	Visit your website URL, and you will be automatically
		redirected to the install script.
-------------------------------------------------------------------
All configuration is done through the administration panel.
